9 |archive-date=2013-10-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-tw |author=劉麗榮 |title=專業受肯定 李翔宙擔國安重任 |publisher=中央社 |location=臺北 |date=2014-05-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-tw |author=尹乃菁 |title=當年李登輝訪美 我方費心護國旗 |publisher=中國時報 |location=臺北 |date=2000-08-15}}</ref>、[[許歷農|許歷農]]、[[周仲南|周仲南]]<ref name="head">{{cite web|language=zh-tw|title=歷任首長|url=http://afrc.mnd.gov.tw/PeopleAmry/AboutAFRC/net_1-3-4.html|location=臺北|publisher=後備指揮部|accessdate=2013-01-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121231223232/http://afrc.mnd.gov.tw/PeopleAmry/AboutAFRC/net_1-3-4.html|archivedate=2012-12-31}}</ref>、[[丁渝洲|丁渝洲]]、[[陳守山|陳守山]]<ref>{{cite web |language=zh |title=永春小估南山陳氏宗親網 |url=http://www.nanchens.com/xqxx/xqxx02/xqxx02045.htm |publisher=永春小估南山陳氏宗親網 |accessdate=2013-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130102232040/http://www.nanchens.com/xqxx/xqxx02/xqxx02045.htm |archive-date=2013-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="head" />、[[馬安瀾|馬安瀾]]、[[薛石民|薛石民]]、[[鄭為元|鄭為元]]、[[羅本立|羅本立]]、[[高華柱|高華柱]]<ref>{{cite web |language=zh-tw |title=高華柱（西元1946～） |url=http://museum.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=1482&p=36878 |location=臺北 |publisher=國軍歷史文物館 |date=2013-08-22 |accessdate=2014-01-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714174846/http://museum.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=1482&p=36878 |archivedate=2014-07-14 }}</ref>等人。

來臺後的陸軍官校專科班僅開辦了27年（期），也產生了二十多名將領，有[[王信龍|王信龍]]（現任國防大學校長）<ref name="dragon"/><ref name="lin1"/>、[[白永成|白永成]]、[[陳健財|陳健財]]<ref name="#3"/>、[[邵定謙|邵定謙]]<ref name="yang">{{cite news|language=zh-tw|url=http://history.n.yam.com/gpwb/life/201101/20110103720849.html|author=劉育然|title=楊天嘯主持裝訓部指揮官布達典禮|publisher=軍聞社|location=臺北|date=2011-01-03|accessdate=2013-03-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714183116/http://history.n.yam.com/gpwb/life/201101/20110103720849.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>、[[黃國明|黃國明]]、[[童盛雄|童盛雄]]、[[楊國隆|楊國隆]]、[[劉木聰|劉木聰]]、[[朱富圓|朱富圓]]、[[張性竹|張性竹]]、[[房茂宏|房茂宏]]<ref>{{cite news|language=zh-tw|url=https://www.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=65&p=68588|author=房茂宏|title=國防部發布「105年上半年將官晉任」|publisher=國防部軍事新聞網|location=臺北|date=2015-12-27|accessdate=2015-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105163339/https://www.mnd.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=65&p=68588|archive-date=2016-01-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-tw |url=http://www.nownews.com/2009/12/28/11490-2551603.htm |author=[[王宗銘|王宗銘]] |title=國防部宣布將官晉任名單 |publisher=今日新聞網 |location=臺北 |date=2009-12-28 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015073925/http://www.nownews.com/2009/12/28/11490-2551603.htm |archive-date=2013-10-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[古勝文|古勝文]]<ref>{{cite news |language=zh-tw |url=http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NAT1/6808988.shtml |author=[[程嘉文|程嘉文]] |title=古勝文 當年貧童今升少將 |publisher=聯合報 |location=臺北 |date=2011-12-28 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014072244/http://udn.com/NEWS/NATIONAL/NAT1/6808988.shtml |archive-date=2013-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-tw |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20111228/33918796/ |author=[[王烱華|王烱華]] |title=將軍晉升 空姐女兒成「嬌點」 |publisher=蘋果日報 |location=臺北 |date=2011-12-28 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819050238/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/headline/20111228/339187