=== 中國共產黨 ===
陸官在實施清黨反共與寧漢分裂前，方有師生以共產黨員身份加入黃埔，其擔任抗戰與國共內戰時知名指揮官有[[左权|左权]]、[[陈赓|陈赓]]<ref name="bio">{{cite web |language=zh-cn |publisher=新华网 |title=陈赓大将的自传 |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2008-02/26/content_7671526.htm |author=陈赓 |location=北京 |date=1944-05 |accessdate=2010年5月30日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418192400/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2008-02/26/content_7671526.htm |archive-date=2010年4月18日 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[徐向前|徐向前]]、[[林彪|林彪]]<ref name="zgg1">{{cite web |language=zh-cn |title=林彪 |url=http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/165618/166491/167905/9974598.html |location=北京 |publisher=人民網 |accessdate=2013-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714145447/http://dangshi.people.com.cn/GB/165617/165618/166491/167905/9974598.html |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[蔣先云|蔣先云]]、[[刘志丹|刘志丹]]、[[罗瑞卿|罗瑞卿]]、[[周士第|周士第]]、[[許光達|許光達]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 | title = 共产党人自身的明镜—许光达大将 | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/120280/8334100.html | location = 北京 | date = 2008-11-19 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063221/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/85037/120280/8334100.html | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |language=zh-cn |publisher=凤凰网 |title=大将许光达的“文革”岁月 |url=http://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200806/0617_2664_601559_2.shtml |author=李意根 |location=北京 |date=2008年6月17日 |accessdate=2010-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100516124232/http://news.ifeng.com/history/1/midang/200806/0617_2664_601559_2.shtml |archive-date=2010年5月16日 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[陳伯鈞|陳伯鈞]]、[[宋时轮|宋时轮]]、[[楊至成|楊至成]]、[[宣侠父|宣侠父]]<ref name="zjw">{{cite news |language=zh-cn |title=出生入死为革命—宣侠父 |publisher=诸暨日报 |location=绍兴 |date=2009-07-16}}</ref>、[[郭天民|郭天民]]、[[陳奇涵|陳奇涵]]、[[陶铸|陶铸]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 人民网 | title = 大事年表（1908年―1928年） | url = http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/69112/113222/113231/index.html | location = 北京 | accessdate = 2010-06-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100824145123/http://cpc.people.com.cn/GB/69112/113222/113231/index.html | archive-date = 2010-08-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[郭汝瑰|郭汝瑰]]<ref name="wenshijinghua">{{cite journal zh |language=zh-cn |author=丁群 |title=最大的共谍”郭汝瑰 |journal=文史精华 |issue=5 |date=2004 |pages=28-35}}</ref>等人。

